<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Boon" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Boon,</orth> a favour begged or granted: <cit><quote>a smaller b. than this I cannot beg,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 5.4.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. V, 4, 24</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to grant one b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 5.4.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. V, 4, 24</bibl></cit> <bibl n="shak. r2 4.302" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 302</bibl>. <emph>you will take exceptions to my b.</emph> (i. e. to the b. which I'll ask) <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.2.46" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 2, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.219" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 219</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.1.95" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 95</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.289" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 289</bibl>. <cit><quote>my b. I make it that you know me not,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 4.7.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 7, 10</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.76" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 76</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 5, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 5, 97</bibl> <bibl n="shak. per 5.2.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. V, 2, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 5.2.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. V, 2, 3</bibl>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>